author: ekoneil
msg: In SVN 47202, the distribution of the NetUI webapp runtime got less aggressive in how it removed JARs from webapps that need to delete NetUI.  As a result, callers need to make sure they cleanup their own JARs as needed.
This change makes that fix for the NetUI coreWeb DRTs so that the test recorder JARs don't exist in the webapp.
